name: BMO Global Enhanced Income Fund
longDescription: The fund investing primarily in a diversified portfolio of global equity exchange traded funds that are higher yielding than the broader equity market, with such funds expected to be predominantly or exclusively funds that are managed by us or one of our affiliates or associates. The fund may also invest in other mutual funds or invest directly in individual fixed income and equity securities This funds objective is to provide income and longterm capital growth.
